## AutoResearch Mode

This workspace is running an autonomous research session.

**Read `.autoresearch/program.md` and follow it exactly.**

Key rules:
- NEVER stop to ask the human — they may be asleep
- NEVER modify files outside the target list in program.md
- ALWAYS record results to the journal before deciding keep/revert
- If a run crashes, log it and move on to the next experiment
- If you run out of ideas, think harder: re-read target files, try combining
  previous near-misses, try more radical changes, decompose the problem
